ឧត្តម</td>\n			<td>ប</td>\n			<td>ម៉ៅសេទុង</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៩០៤</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>៦</td>\n			<td>តេង គីមស័ង</td>\n			<td>ស</td>\n			<td>ម៉ៅសេទុង</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៨៤៨</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>៧</td>\n			<td>ឆាយ ឈុនលី</td>\n			<td>ប</td>\n			<td>ម៉ៅសេទុង</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៨៤៣</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>៨</td>\n			<td>លាង ប៉ូលីនណា</td>\n			<td>ស</td>\n			<td>ម៉ៅសេទុង</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៨៤៣</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>៩</td>\n			<td>លី ឌីនីកា</td>\n			<td>ស</td>\n			<td>ទួលគោក</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៨២៣</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>១០</td>\n			<td>អេង លីបណ្ឌិត</td>\n			<td>ប</td>\n			<td>ម៉ៅសេទុង</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៨០៨</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>១១</td>\n			<td>លឹម ឈីវហ៊ុង</td>\n			<td>ស</td>\n			<td>ម៉ៅសេទុង</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៧៧៥</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>១២</td>\n			<td>សុខ ហ៊្សុយអេង</td>\n			<td>ស</td>\n			<td>ម៉ៅសេទុង</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៧៣៤</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>១៣</td>\n			<td>ហេង គីមហុង</td>\n			<td>ប</td>\n			<td>ទួលគោក</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៦៩៦</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>១៤</td>\n			<td>ឈូក ច័ន្ទធីតា</td>\n			<td>ស</td>\n			<td>ម៉ៅសេទុង</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៦៨០</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>១៥</td>\n			<td>ទូច សុបញ្ញា</td>\n			<td>ប</td>\n			<td>ម៉ៅសេទុង</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៦៨០</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>១៦</td>\n			<td>ហួរ គឹមស៊ីន</td>\n			<td>ស</td>\n			<td>ទួលគោក</td>\n			<td>៩៩.៦៤៧</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><strong>ថ្ងៃទី២៦ កញ្ញា ដល់០៥ តុលា ២០១៧</strong></p>\n\n<p>ក្រុមកីឡាបាល់បោះនារី អន្តរទ្វីប ត្រូវបានមន្ទីរអប់រំ យុវជន និងកីឡារាជធានីភ្នំពេញ ជ្រើសរើសជាតំណាងរាជធានី ឱ្យចូលរួមការប្រកួតកីឡាសិស្សជ្រើសរើសជើងឯកទូទាំងប្រទេស និងកីឡាអត្តពលកម្ម នៅទីរួមខេត្តកំពង់ចាម៖</p>\n\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<th>ល.រ.</th>\n			<th>គោត្ដនាម-នាម</th>\n			<th>ថ្នាក់ទី</th>\n			<th>វិញ្ញាសា</th>\n			<th>ប្រភេទ</th>\n			<th>ចំ.លេខ</th>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>១</td>\n			<td>សំណាង វីរៈបុត្រ</td>\n			<td>១១ក</td>\n			<td>វាយកូនឃ្លីលើតុបុរស</td>\n			<td>ឯកត្តជន</td>\n			<td>១</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>២</td>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td>១០ច</td>\n			<td>វាយកូនឃ្លីលើតុបុរស</td>\n			<td>ឯកត្តជន</td>\n			<td>២</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">៣</td>\n			<td>សំណាង វីរៈបុត្រ</td>\n			<td>១១ក</td>\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">វាយកូនឃ្លីលើតុបុរស</td>\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">ក្រុម</td>\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">១</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>ទួន គីផាត់</td>\n			<td>១០ច</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>៤</td>\n			<td colspan=\"3\">ក្រុមកីឡាបាល់បោះនារី អន្តរទ្វីប</td>\n			<td>ក្រុម</td>\n			<td>២</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><strong>ថ្ងៃទី៣០ កញ្ញា ២០១៧</strong></p>\n\n<p>យុវសិស្ស ថាវរៈ ប៊ុណ្ណវឌ្ឍនៈ ថ្នាក់ទី៦ &ldquo;ឃ&rdquo; និងយុវសិស្ស ថៃ ឈីច ថ្នាក់ទី១០ &ldquo;ខ&rdquo; នៃសាលារៀន អន្តរទ្វីប អាមេរិកាំង ទទួលបានជ័យលាភីក្នុងកម្មវិធីប្រកួតគណិតវិទ្យា SUKEN Test Cambodia 2017 ដែលរៀបចំឡើងដោយ STEAM Cambodia នៅសាកលវិទ្យាល័យ ហ្សាម៉ាន់។</p>\n\n<p><strong>ថ្ងៃទី១៤ តុលា ២០១៧</strong></p>\n\n<p>កុមារី សម្បត្តិ សិរីកា ថ្នាក់ទី៤ &ldquo;ក&rdquo; នៃសាលារៀន អន្តរទ្វីប អាមេរិកាំង ទទួលបានជ័យលាភីមេដាយមាសក្នុងការប្រកួត American Mathematics Olympiad Cambodia 2017 ជាមួយបណ្តាប្រទេសនៅអាស៊ី។</p>\n\n<p><strong>ថ្ងៃទី០២&ndash;១៨ ធ្នូ ២០១៧</strong></p>\n\n<p>ក្រុមកីឡាបាល់បោះនារី អន្តរទ្វីប ទទួលបានជ័យលាភីចំណាត់ថ្នាក់លេខ២ ក្នុងការប្រកួតកីឡាបាល់បោះជ្រើសរើសជើងឯកយុវជនក្រោមអាយុ១៨ឆ្នាំ ប្រចាំឆ្នាំ២០១៧ ដែលរៀបចំដោយសហព័ន្ធកីឡាបាល់បោះកម្ពុជានៅវិទ្យាល័យព្រះស៊ីសុវត្ថិ។</p>', '<p><strong>October 14, 2017</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS student won the Gold Medal in the American Math Olympiad Cambodia 2017, a competition between ASEAN countries.</p>\n\n<p><strong>December 02-18, 2017</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS Female Basketball Team won 2nd place in the U18 Basketball Competition organized by Cambodia Basketball Federation.</p>\n\n<p><strong>January 25-28, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS student won the Writing Competition in Astronomy and was selected to represent Cambodia to compete in the ASEAN Astronmy Camping 2018 organized by The National Astronomical Research Institute of Thailand in Chiang Mai, Thailand.</p>\n\n<p><strong>February 09, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS student won the awards in the International Music and Song Contest, Asia Pacific Arts Festival organized in Siem Reap and Singapore (many Asian counties participated).</p>\n\n<p><strong>February 20-24, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS Female Basketball team was selected by Cambodia Basketball Federation to represent Cambodia for a Friendly Match of International U18 with all countries along the Mekong River, Champasak, Laos Republic.</p>\n\n<p><strong>February 27-March 05, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS Female Basketball Team won 2nd place in the Phnom Penh Secondary School Sport Competition organized by MoEYS.</p>\n\n<p><strong>February 27-March 05, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS Male Basketball Team won 3rd place in the Phnom Penh Secondary School Sport Competition organized by MoEYS.</p>\n\n<p><strong>February 27-March 05, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS students won 1st and 2nd in Phom Penh Multi-Sport Competition organized by MoEYS.</p>\n\n<p><strong>February 27-March 05, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS Table Tennis team won 1st place in the Phnom Penh Secondary School Sport Competition organized by MoEYS.</p>\n\n<p><strong>March 07, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS students won 1st and 2nd palce in the Phnom Penh Manucipality Outstanding Student Examination organzied by MoEYS.</p>\n\n<p><strong>April 20, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>3 AIS students were won 3rd and 4th place in Drawing competition under a theme: &ldquo;New Perception toward the World&rdquo; at the International Secondary School Arts Festival 2018, national level, held at University of Cambodia.</p>\n\n<p><strong>April 21, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>2 AIS students were won the Silver Medal and Bronze Medal in Singapore and ASIAN School Math Olympiad SASMO 2018.</p>\n\n<p><strong>April 23, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS students won the 4th place in the Nationwide Physics Outstanding Student Examination organzied by MoEYS.</p>\n\n<p><strong>May 05-14, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS Table Tennis team won 1st place in the National Champion Competition and Athletic Sport at Kampot province organzied by MoEYS.</p>\n\n<p><strong>July 05, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>American Intercon School was awarded by MoEYS as the top leading school in Management, Education Administration, Quality of Teaching and best Environment in Phnom Penh in Academic Year 2017-2018.</p>\n\n<p><strong>July 18-27, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>8 AIS Students were selected by Behring Global Educational Foundation to participate in the Global Natural History Day 2018 (GNHD), Finals in Chongqing City, China and won the 4 Gold Medals and 2 Silvers.</p>\n\n<p><strong>July 18-27, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>2 AIS Students won 2 Gold Medals in the 2018 Global Learning Across Borders (LAB) with with other 10 ASEAN countries and USA in Laos Republic.</p>\n\n<p><strong>July 27-31, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>AIS students was won the Bronze Medal in The International Junior Math Olympiad (IJMO), Thailand 2018.</p>\n\n<p><strong>August 13, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>Highest passing rate (100%) in the Junior High School National Examination.</p>\n\n<p><strong>August 20, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>23 AIS Grade A Studnets High School National Examination.</p>\n\n<p><strong>September 27, 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>Mr. Puthpanha Soeung, Grade 12B was ranked #3 in Asia Network of Exchange for Students and Youths (JENESYS 2018)</p>', 1, NULL, NULL, '2022-08-18 06:25:05', '2022-09-16 07:04:01');
INSERT INTO `events` (`id`, `title_kh`, `title_en`, `feature`, `parent_category_id`, `slug`, `date_kh`, `date_en`, `expire_date`, `description_kh`, `description_en`, `state`, `start_date`, `end_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(16, '2014', 'Academic Year 2014-2015', 0, 1, 'academic-year-2014-2015', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>ថ្ងៃទី១១ មករា ២០១៤</strong></p>\n\n<p>យុវសិស្ស ផាង ម៉ូលីតា យុវសិស្ស ស្រី ច័ន្ទផល និងយុវសិស្ស រ័ត្ន ប៉ោថេង ថ្នាក់ទី១២ក នៃសាលារៀន អន្ដរទ្វីប អាមេរិកាំង ទទួលបានជ័យលាភីចំណាត់ថ្នាក់លេខ៣ ក្នុងការប្រកួត ការតាំងពិព័រណ៍ថ្នាក់ជាតិ ស្តីពីវិទ្យាសាស្រ្ត និងវិស្វកម្ម របស់សាកលវិទ្យាល័យហ្សាម៉ាន់ ដឹកនាំដោយ លោកគ្រូ ប៉ឹក ប៊ុនបញ្ញា គ្រូបង្រៀនរូបវិទ្យា លើប្រធានបទស្តីអំពី Stirling Engine ក្នុងការចូលរួម ប្រឡងដោយប្រើប្រាស់ជាភាសាអង់គ្លេស ក្នុងការធ្វើបទបង្ហាញ ក្នុងនោះរង្វាន់ទទួលបានមានបណ្ណ សរសើរ និងទឹកប្រាក់ចំនួន៥០០,០០០ (ហាសិបម៉ឺនរៀល) និងគ្រូដឹកនាំទទួលបានទឹកប្រាក់ចំនួន៤០០,០០០ (សែសិបម៉ឺនរៀល)។</p>\n\n<p><strong>ថ្ងៃទី២៤-២៧ កុម្ភៈ ២០១៤</strong></p>\n\n<p>សិស្សចំនួន០៨រូប នៃសាលារៀន អន្ដរទ្វីប អាមេរិកាំង ទទួលបានជ័យលាភីក្នុងការប្រកួតកីឡាសិស្សបឋម និងមធ្យមសិក្សាជ្រើសរើសជើងឯករាជធានីភ្នំពេញ ប្រចាំឆ្នាំ សិក្សា២០១៣-២០១៤ រៀបចំដោយមន្ទីរអប់រំ យុវជន និងកីឡារាជធានីភ្នំពេញ៖</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp